The dockers have also bolstered their ranks with the acquisition of Equity Bank star forward Ritah AluochAnthony Ojukwu, who has returned as head coach after a year's break, believes they can win all the trophies on offer this seasonAccording to Ojukwu, the decision by KPA's management to ensure all players train together in Mombasa will help build the chemistry in the team which has been lacking in the past